Forces Boothill and a single target enemy into the Standoff state. Boothill's Basic ATK gets Enhanced, and he cannot use his Skill, lasting for #3[i] turn(s). This duration decreases by 1 at the start of Boothill's every turn.The enemy target in the Standoff becomes Taunted. When this enemy target/Boothill gets attacked by the other party in the Standoff, the DMG they receive increases by #1[i]%/#2[i]%.After this target is defeated or becomes Weakness Broken, Boothill gains 1 stack of Pocket Trickshot, then dispels the Standoff.This Skill cannot regenerate Energy. After using this Skill, the current turn does not end.
